@startuml
title Viaverse Search / SEO / Indexing — Sequence Diagram

actor "Client / Guest" as Client
participant "API Gateway / Web BFF" as BFF
participant "search-service" as Search
participant "AI intent service" as AI
database "OpenSearch" as OpenSearch
participant "trust-gamification" as Trust
participant "analytics-service" as Analytics
queue "Kafka / Outbox" as Kafka

Client -> BFF : GET /search?q=...
BFF -> Search : search(command)
Search -> AI : optional intent/category
Search -> OpenSearch : geo/category/full-text query
Search -> Trust : trust/risk summaries
Search -> Search : rank + privacy gates + sponsored after gates
Search -> Analytics : impression event
Search --> BFF : result cards + reason hints
BFF --> Client : render results

Kafka -> Search : EntityPublished / Updated / Removed
Search -> OpenSearch : update search projection

note bottom
Search-service owns projections and ranking.
It consumes public entity events; source-of-truth remains domain services.
end note
@enduml
